name: Torchic Head
description:
this is a cuphead fangame ._.
Player 1: use asd to move. W or E to Jump. Q to Shoot
Player 2: Use arrow keys to move. Up arrow or N to Jump. M to Shoot

if your playing in single player then use Z or Up arrow to jump. X to shoot

X to shoot

Z to jump

this game might make you rage ._.
